snippet.title: "Fantastic Beasts Will Fail" J.K. Rowling Finally Reacts To Losing Johnny Depp (VIDEO)
snippet.description:
"Fantastic Beasts Will Fail" J.K. Rowling Finally Reacts To Losing Johnny Depp (VIDEO)
In this video, Film Streak Showcases J.K Rowling's Reaction to Losing Johnny Depp in the upcoming Fantastic Beasts And Where To Find Them Movie. As you know, Johnny has been replaced by Mads Mikkelsen and according to J.K. Rowling, this can literally destroy the movie series! 

Here on Film Streak, we are all about the latest spill in Hollywood! You can rest assured that we will bring you all the latest celebrity drama and gossip especially concerning your favorite actors! We´ll also make sure to keep you updated on the newest movie updates and releases – so if you are interested in anything that happens in Hollywood, you should make sure to stay tuned!  

And there you have it guys! We hope you enjoyed the video! If you did please consider leaving a like and telling us what you though in the comments!
